  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the demographic characteristics of patients suffering from mental retardation or
      cerebral palsy in the Israeli Arab community. Specific questionnaires will be developed and
      will be distributed amongst this population in order to identify these characteristics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
